post_summaries.description: The image is a screenshot of an Instagram post by user gshishya. The post consists of a graphic with two overlapping speech bubbles, one green and one blue. Superimposed on the graphic is text in Hindi that asks people to send a message with their name, location, photo, address, and problem so the poster can help them in a short amount of time.

The image is a painting of the Hindu goddess Durga riding a tiger on top of a buffalo demon. The text in the image translates to "Mother Durga will remove your big problems with this remedy." The post's caption also discusses solving problems and mentions upcoming videos.
The image shows a hand receiving a stack of Indian Rupees (2000 denomination). The text overlay in Hindi translates to "Tips to get rid of debt."

The image is a post on Instagram by "gshishya" featuring a depiction of the Hindu goddess Kali standing on top of Shiva. The post also includes text in Hindi that translates to something like "Any problem, trouble, calamity, will be removed in a snap with the remedies of Kali Maa". The post also includes a link to a video.

The image is a cartoon-style illustration of a man, presumably a "Tantrik" (as indicated in the post's caption and text in the image), sitting in a meditative pose with a fire burning in front of him. He is also holding a phone to his ear. There's a skull and other ritualistic items present. The text in the image translates to "Tantrik and my channel" and the logo "Guru Shishya" is also visible.

The image is a post on Instagram by gshishya. It features an image of the goddess Lakshmi and text in Hindi that translates to "Lakshmi Prapti Ke Teen Achuk Totke" which means "Three Sure Remedies for Attaining Lakshmi (Prosperity)."
